"{\"uid\": \"inews.co.uk-sport-olympics-why-olympic-surfing-taking-place-10000-miles-from-paris-makes-perfect-sense-3193157\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"IMPARTIAL NEWS + INTELLIGENT DEBATE Account The world's best surfers will compete for gold on the largest island in French Polynesia despite concerns about the environmental impact PARIS - There are no consistent surf spots close to Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 125, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9969176049385164, \"rank\": 0.003091925597809543, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}, {\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.701976770639334e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NEWS\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 14}, {\"ngram\": \"The world's best surfers\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 68}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"the largest island\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 149}, {\"ngram\": \"the environmental impact\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 180}, {\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nearest are in and around Biarritz and Hossegor, just north of the Basque country, close to the Spanish border - around 500 miles away from the French capital.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biarritz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999572537, \"rank\": 4.276667431694255e-11, \"text\": \"Biarritz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biarritz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Biarritz\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soorts-Hossegor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hossegor\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soorts-Hossegor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soorts-Hossegor\"}, {\"begin\": 314, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Basque_Country\", \"score\": 0.6736793928111647, \"rank\": 0.47743014744623274, \"text\": \"Basque\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Basque_Country\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Basque_Country\"}, {\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.923815202793478, \"rank\": 0.07070400421765015, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 391, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6734832034565019, \"rank\": 0.38603877612022736, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But they are a darn sight closer than Tahiti, where theParis 2024surfing competition is being held.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.999915735897709, \"rank\": 8.427120341076335e-05, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theParis 2024surfing competition\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The choice of Teahupo'o as the venue forthe Olympic Gamesappeared at first glance the epitome of French haughtiness - we have the world's best spot in one of our colonies and,Mon Dieu, we are going to exploit it.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6734832034565019, \"rank\": 0.38603877612022736, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue forthe Olympic Gamesappeared\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"first glance\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the epitome\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best spot\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"our colonies\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a decision that was met with enthusiasm by the athletes, especially those who are not of the calibre of those inthe World Surf League, the top-level competition circuit.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.666629936728329e-24, \"text\": \"World Surf League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"enthusiasm\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"especially those\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"the calibre\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"the top-level competition circuit\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was far less popular among locals.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Resistance to the Olympic circus coming to town for the weekend grew when the International Olympic Committee (IOC) announced that it needed to build a more permanent judging tower than the temporary wooden one that had been built and dismantled yearly since the early 2000s.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Resistance\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic circus\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekend\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"a more permanent judging tower\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"the temporary wooden one\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said the tower needed to be made of aluminium and required air-conditioning and toilets.\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.965194271276124e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tower\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"aluminium\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"required air-conditioning\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"toilets\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that it needed to be built on the fragile coral reef just out of reach of the wave.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fragile coral reef\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"reach\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Resistance came from the biggest name in the sport, Kelly Slater, who said last year: \\\"It does not make sense to build such a huge tower for a two-day event.\\\"\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Slater\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Slater\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Resistance\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest name\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"such a huge tower\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-day event\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the residents of the village on the shore had legitimate fears that their way of life would be irrevocably changed.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the residents\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"the shore\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"legitimate fears\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is far from a surf resort - there is not even a surf shop there, let alone an apres-surf bar.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a surf resort\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"a surf shop\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"an apres-surf bar\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Newquay it is not.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peva Levy, a Teahupo'o resident one of the first to surf the spot, said: \\\"It was too much for us, a big change.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peva Levy\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"the spot\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"a big change\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was just for, like, one week.\\\"\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Teahupo'o (pronounced te-ah-hu-poh'oh and loosely translated to \\\"place of skulls\\\") is an awe-inspiring location, to give Paris 2024 organisers their due.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2076, \"end\": 2086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1655688709498848e-27, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"te-ah-hu-poh'oh\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"place\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"skulls\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"an awe-inspiring location\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And although it is roughly 10,000 miles from Paris, the impact of flying 48 surfers there is not as great as if they had flown to France, as the majority of competitors are from Pacific Rim and South American countries.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2155, \"end\": 2160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.701976770639334e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999986553002546, \"rank\": 1.339077585412872e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.987323316779923, \"rank\": 0.01283944455409369, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2172}, {\"ngram\": \"48 surfers\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two of France's four representatives are from French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2337, \"end\": 2343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999986553002546, \"rank\": 1.339077585412872e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"French Polynesia\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One lives in Reunion - hardly a short hop from Paris.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2441, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.701976770639334e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One lives\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"Reunion\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"hardly a short hop\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wave itself is mesmerising, if also deadly - it appears to bend laws of physics on big swells.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wave\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2457}, {\"ngram\": \"laws\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"physics\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"big swells\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A huge wall of blue liquid rises out of the deep, the lip feathers in the offshore wind, before the wall bends, curls and explodes on the shallow water covering a reef, creating a tube wider than it is high.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A huge wall\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"blue liquid\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2575}, {\"ngram\": \"the offshore wind\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall bends\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"curls\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"explodes\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"the shallow water\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"a reef\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"a tube\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sea level drops by at least two feet in the vortex of the chaos.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sea level\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"at least two feet\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"the vortex\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"the chaos\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian world No 5 Ethan Ewing, who broke his back in a wipeout at Teahupo'o in August 2023, said: \\\"The energy of this wave is like nothing else.\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2827, \"end\": 2837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999998099651929, \"rank\": 1.7350902948913683e-07, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No 5 Ethan Ewing\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"his back\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"a wipeout\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"The energy\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"this wave\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just so raw and has so much power.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much power\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even now there are still nerves.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nerves\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just one of those waves, it's got big consequences.\\\"\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those waves\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"big consequences\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But a few days of beautiful images was going to come at a massive cost to the local environment and the people who live there every day.\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3126}, {\"ngram\": \"beautiful images\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive cost\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"the local environment\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So the IOC scaled back its plans.\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3257, \"end\": 3260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.965194271276124e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its plans\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where it was going to build an athletes' village for the 48 surfers and their respective medical and support staff, it now houses them on a cruise ship berthed offshore.\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athletes' village\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3332}, {\"ngram\": \"the 48 surfers\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective medical and support staff\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3398}, {\"ngram\": \"a cruise ship\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the tower is now collapsible, like the previous one.\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tower\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been placed in the same spot as the old one - where there is minimal coral growth, according to surf photographer Tim McKenna, who visited Teahupo'o just before the final test event before the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3721, \"e